1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 14=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,110
We used the phoenix pearl pattern

4
00:00:59,110 --> 00:01:00,350
to name the eight chambers.

5
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,560
But the Dui chamber shows Kun.

6
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,480
The Li chamber shows Gen.

7
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,950
(Zhen, Xun)
The Zhen chamber shows Xun.

8
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:09,560
Only the Kan chamber points to Kan.

9
00:01:09,763 --> 00:01:11,510
Among the eight chambers
we passed through,

10
00:01:11,510 --> 00:01:13,443
the compass needle was chaotic
in four chambers.

11
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,760
Only four chambers pointed
to the correct directions.

12
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,870
Just like you said,

13
00:01:17,070 --> 00:01:18,760
Kun, Gen, Xun, and Kan.

14
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,086
There are only four directions.

15
00:01:21,370 --> 00:01:22,380
Where are the other four?

16
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,790
We fell from above.

17
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:31,683
That means the other four directions

18
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:34,950
should be below.

19
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,150
In other words,

20
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,960
there is another space underneath.

21
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,990
If this plane only has four directions,

22
00:01:40,001 --> 00:01:42,245
it is not arranged according
to Fu Xi's Primordial Bagua

23
00:01:42,256 --> 00:01:43,493
or King Wen's Manifested Bagua.

24
00:01:43,656 --> 00:01:45,070
It must follow the Qian Kun diagram,

25
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,510
the 3D Bagua arrangement.

26
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,613
Using the compass needle
as the reference,

27
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:54,120
the directions corresponding below are

28
00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:00,430
Dui, Zhen, Qian, and Li.

29
00:02:01,802 --> 00:02:04,029
The planar Bagua derived
from the phoenix pearl pattern

30
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,686
and the 3D Bagua indicated
by the compass

31
00:02:05,697 --> 00:02:07,150
overlap in only one chamber.

32
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,000
In other words,

33
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,120
the Kan chamber is this chamber.

34
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,993
Kan belongs to water
and represents the north.

35
00:02:18,063 --> 00:02:19,743
The mechanism
should be on the north side.

36
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,430
Buddy, buddy.

37
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,310
Buddy.

38
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,190
Calm down.

39
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,960
I was tricked too.

40
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,000
I got separated.

41
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:55,150
How about this?

42
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,190
I will work for you.

43
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,710
I will serve you.

44
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,800
- No.
- Where is my box?

45
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,560
I didn't take that box.

46
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:05,000
Buddy, Chubby took it.

47
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,150
Where did they run off to?

48
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:07,000
Chubby

49
00:03:07,850 --> 00:03:08,690
ran that way.

50
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:09,870
The woman ran that way.

51
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,000
Where could they possibly go?

52
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,360
How would I know?

53
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:14,030
My guess is

54
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:16,630
they took that big box to find a buyer.

55
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,520
How did Lu get captured?

56
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,400
He tried to save me.

57
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,680
Look at Huang Long.

58
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,310
Lu exposing himself like that

59
00:03:26,310 --> 00:03:27,590
was basically suicide.

60
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,870
Buddy, calm down.

61
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,430
I understand this. I run a shop.

62
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:31,910
That box is not worth much.

63
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,080
The real valuables are with you.

64
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,200
Well.

65
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,360
Like this jar.

66
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,470
Let me make an appraisal,

67
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,310
so you can sell it at a high price.

68
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,400
It looks like

69
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,310
this is the real Qian chamber.

70
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,590
The exit should be
behind one of these doors.

71
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:04,800
This tomb has an exquisite structure
and massive scale.

72
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,093
It could be developed
into a tourist attraction.

73
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,190
Who'd come to a tomb for tourism?

74
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:31,510
Jade, jade artifacts,
gold and silver treasures.

75
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:36,390
Farming tools and grain.

76
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:39,360
Musical instruments and pottery jars.

77
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,320
A scale.

78
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,440
An hourglass.

79
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,560
This is not the exit.

80
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,880
This is a mechanism.

81
00:05:21,976 --> 00:05:23,270
If all those arrows fire at once,

82
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,536
even ten of us wouldn't survive.

83
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,360
The hourglass is the timer.

84
00:05:26,371 --> 00:05:27,589
If we can't solve the mechanism

85
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,480
within a certain time,

86
00:05:28,630 --> 00:05:29,920
I am afraid we will be doomed.

87
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,560
Where did they go?

88
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,750
Why are you so angry?

89
00:05:34,050 --> 00:05:34,910
Look.

90
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:36,120
Everything here is fine.

91
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,240
Even the oranges fell.

92
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,080
Shut up.

93
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,600
If you don't tell me where they went,

94
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,040
I will blow your head off.

95
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,583
But you told me to shut up.

96
00:05:48,594 --> 00:05:50,607
How am I supposed to tell you
where they are then?

97
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,560
I will kill you.

98
00:06:03,170 --> 00:06:04,010
Wait, wait.

99
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,040
Lu, run.

100
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,760
Go.

101
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,320
Lu, hurry.

102
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,230
Don't move.

103
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,480
This is a linked mechanism.

104
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,983
Something must be placed here

105
00:06:35,994 --> 00:06:37,950
to make the mass on both sides
of the scale equal

106
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:39,000
to disable the mechanism.

107
00:06:42,416 --> 00:06:44,229
The items on the table
should be the weights.

108
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,600
But in such a short time,

109
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:47,680
how can we possibly

110
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,280
calculate the exact mass of the weights?

111
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:51,480
Even the slightest error

112
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,446
will cause the arrows to fire.

113
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:54,680
If mass will not work,

114
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,030
what about density?

115
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,040
The statue is carved from rock.

116
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,680
The rock layer here is limestone.

117
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:01,000
Limestone.

118
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:04,070
These are musical instruments,
ceramics, pottery jars,

119
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,000
jade plaques, and jade belts.

120
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,120
There is a horse.

121
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,480
In every chamber we passed through,

122
00:07:08,649 --> 00:07:10,452
the carvings were phoenix
and pearl patterns.

123
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:12,036
Why is it that an inconspicuous statue

124
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,070
was placed

125
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,430
at the most important mechanism?

126
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,040
A statue.

127
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,950
Having fun?

128
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,390
Keep playing.

129
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:27,830
Let us see how you get Ms. He killed.

130
00:07:28,290 --> 00:07:29,150
Huang Long,

131
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,480
release Ms. He now.

132
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,430
Otherwise, I'll blow up the stone box.

133
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:34,870
Go ahead and try.

134
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:37,120
Lu, show him the stone box.

135
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,000
See it?

136
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,390
Do you think I wouldn't dare?

137
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:44,750
All your explosives are in my hands.

138
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,240
In our hands.

139
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,750
Show him the explosives, Lu.

140
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,160
See that?

141
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,880
Don't.

142
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,870
Chubby sure is fierce.

143
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,680
So fierce that he ignores everyone.

144
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,190
What about Ms. He's life?

145
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,360
Cut the nonsense.

146
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,800
Release Ms. He now.

147
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,070
Sure, I can release her.

148
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,480
Give me the box.

149
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:09,790
Chubby,

150
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,920
why bother?

151
00:08:12,310 --> 00:08:14,190
It is just a box. Just give it to him.

152
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,270
Why fight over it?

153
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,190
Stop talking nonsense.

154
00:08:16,201 --> 00:08:17,129
If we give him the box,

155
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:18,160
how will Ms. He escape?

156
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,310
What do you suggest then?

157
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,000
Huang Long,

158
00:08:31,870 --> 00:08:33,030
release Ms. He.

159
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:34,960
We will leave immediately.

160
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:37,150
We mind our own business.

161
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:39,910
Otherwise, we will fight to the death.

162
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:41,960
Fine.

163
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,670
Deal?

164
00:08:43,790 --> 00:08:44,840
Deal.

165
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,320
A statue.

166
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,670
The statue represents the tomb builder.

167
00:09:14,313 --> 00:09:15,559
If we think from another angle,

168
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,600
jade, jade artifacts,

169
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,630
pearls, and treasures represent wealth.

170
00:09:21,552 --> 00:09:23,375
Bamboo slips, brush, ink,
paper, and inkstone

171
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,510
represent wisdom.

172
00:09:26,033 --> 00:09:27,109
Jade plaques and jade belts

173
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,150
represent power.

174
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,750
By placing himself
on one side of the scale,

175
00:09:34,206 --> 00:09:35,750
the tomb builder is asking the visitor

176
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:37,326
what his life's achievements were worth

177
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:38,960
and how much value

178
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,790
his life held.

179
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,840
Chubby, light it.

180
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,080
Watch out!

181
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,200
Run!

182
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:49,630
Chen, hurry!

183
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:51,150
I'm cutting off your path.

184
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,000
- Go, Lu.
- Lu, hurry.

185
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,910
- My box.
- Go.

186
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,870
Forget the box.

187
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:03,870
My box.

188
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,510
Bomb!

189
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:53,510
This jerk is everywhere.

190
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,240
How is it? Are you hurt?

191
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:00,030
How is it? Are you okay?

192
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:02,590
I am fine too.

193
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:03,590
I am fine.

194
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:04,480
Go. Retreat.

195
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,320
Retreat. Hurry.

196
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:30,870
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

197
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:36,230
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

198
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:41,870
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

199
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:49,020
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

200
00:13:49,580 --> 00:14:00,600
♪La la♪

201
00:14:07,350 --> 00:14:09,340
♪No line divides the border♪

202
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:12,120
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

203
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:14,490
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

204
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:17,180
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

205
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:20,390
♪Hey hey hey♪

206
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,540
♪Hey hey hey♪

207
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:27,190
♪Hey hey♪

208
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:28,340
♪Hey hey♪

209
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:30,880
♪Hey hey♪

210
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:36,710
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

211
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:41,010
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

212
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:45,510
♪No difference between you and me♪

213
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:48,120
♪No lead or side role on this stage♪

214
